---
import Layout from "../layouts/WMBase.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/Breadcrumbs.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | Window Maintenance Wellington";
const description = "How Window Maintenance collects, uses and protects your information when you request a quote or use our Wellington window and door repair website.";
const canonical = "https://windowmaintenance.co.nz/privacy/";
const updated = "24 June 2026";
---
<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Breadcrumbs />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-8 leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      <section>
        <p>This policy explains how Window Maintenance ("we", "us") collects, uses and protects your personal information when you contact us or use this website. We handle personal information in accordance with the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Who we are</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">Window Maintenance is an aluminium window and door repair business serving the Wellington region.</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
          <li>Phone: <a class="text-blue-600 underline" href="tel:+6421638205">021 638 205</a></li>
          <li>Email: <a class="text-blue-600 underline" href="mailto:baeley@windowmaintenance.co.nz">baeley@windowmaintenance.co.nz</a></li>
          <li>NZBN: 9429052805455</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Information we collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong class="text-slate-900">Information you give us.</strong> When you submit a quote or contact form, we collect your name, phone number, and (if you provide them) your email address, suburb, a description of the work, and any photos you choose to send. We use this only to respond to your enquiry, provide a quote, and arrange the work.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong class="text-slate-900">Information collected automatically.</strong> Like most websites, we collect standard technical and usage information (such as pages viewed, approximate location, device and browser type) through analytics and advertising tools so we can understand how the site is used and measure our advertising. This is described under "Cookies and tracking" below.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Cookies and tracking</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">This site uses the following third-party tools, which may set cookies or use similar technologies:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Google Analytics 4</strong> — to measure website traffic and usage.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Google Ads conversion tracking</strong>, including <em>enhanced conversions</em>. When you submit a form, a hashed (encrypted) version of the email address or phone number you entered may be sent to Google to help measure the performance of our advertising. Google processes this in hashed form.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Ahrefs Analytics</strong> — privacy-focused website analytics.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We also use your browser's local storage to remember that you have recently sent us a form, so we can avoid asking you to submit twice. This stays on your device.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">You can control or delete cookies through your browser settings, and you can manage Google's use of advertising data at <a class="text-blue-600 underline" href="https://myadcenter.google.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">myadcenter.google.com</a>. Blocking cookies will not stop you from using the site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Who we share it with</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">We do not sell your personal information. We share it only with service providers who help us run the site and respond to you:</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
          <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Formspree</strong> — delivers our contact form submissions to us by email.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Google</strong> — analytics and advertising measurement.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Ahrefs</strong> — website analytics.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">Some of these providers are based overseas, which means your information may be stored or processed outside New Zealand.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">How long we keep it</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">We keep enquiry details for as long as needed to respond to you and for our ordinary business and tax record-keeping requirements, after which we delete or anonymise them.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Your rights</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">Under the Privacy Act 2020 you can ask to see the personal information we hold about you and request that we correct it. Contact us using the details above and we will respond as soon as we reasonably can.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-3">We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be on this page with the date it was last updated.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
